---
title: Chicken Meatball Gnocchi with Sage, Apple and Spinach
description: These chicken meatballs are super flavourful thanks to our secret ingredients: grated apples and carrots! Together with gnocchi, baked apple slices, spinach and sage, this makes for a delicious meal for the entire family!
